Package: logtail
Title: Log transformation to visualize tail latencies
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jeremias",
           family = "Blendin",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "github@jgjl.de")
Description: Creates a log transformation which focusses on the increasing side of values.
             This is the inverse behavior of what log transformations do by default. This
             kind of transformation is useful when investigating latency distributions.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/jgjl/taillog
BugReports: https://github.com/jgjl/taillog/issues
Depends: 
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0.9000)
Imports: 
    scales
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
